PrecisAppointment of Suzanne Laporte as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Niger; Manfred G. Von Nostitz as Ambassador of Canada to the Union of Myanmar; Colleen Swords as High Commissioner for Canada to Grenada and as Commissiner for Canada to Anguilla, British Virgin Islands and Montserrat; Jean-Paul Hubert as Ambassador of Canada to the Grand Duchy of Luxembourg; Wilfrid-Guy Licari as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Cape Verde, the Republic of Guinea, and the Islamic Republic of Mauritania as well as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of the Gambia; Marc Brault as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Mauritius; Verona Edelstein as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Seychelles as well as Ambassador of Canada to the Democratic Republic of Madagascar; Garrett C.M. Lambert as Consul General of Canada to Macao; Louise Fortin as Ambassador of Canada to the Democratic Republic of Sao Tome and Principe and to the People's Republic of the Congo, as well as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Equatorial Guinea; Alain Dudoit as Ambassador of Canada to the Slovak Republic; Robert A. Wright as High Commissioner for Canada to the Kingdom of Tonga, the Independent State of Western Samoa, Kiribati, and Tuvalu, as well as Ambassador of Canada to Fiji; John Noble as Consul General of Canada to the Principality of Monaco; and John Schram as Ambassador of Canada to the Togolese Republic.
